·ServiceSubmitted(project_id, version, service_tag, evidence_bundle_hash, participant_ref, root_id, lease_id, time_completed, ...) ·ServiceConfirmed(project_id, version, service_tag, verifier_id, result=ACCEPT, ...) ·PSA-1 输出的 points_count / captured_count / missing_count / sampling_commit_hash / sampling_compliance_status 等事实字段。
